sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Client as External Client
    participant IstioGW as Istio Ingress Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Proxy as Model Registry Proxy<br/>8080/TCP HTTP (Istio mTLS)
    participant DB as MySQL/PostgreSQL<br/>3306/5432/TCP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Controller as MR Controller<br/>8081/TCP (health)
    participant CSI as MR CSI Init Container
    participant KServePod as KServe Predictor Pod
    participant AsyncJob as Async Upload Job
    participant S3 as S3 / Object Store<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Sigstore as Sigstore<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,DB: Flow 1: Model Registration via REST API

    Client->>IstioGW: POST /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/registered_models<br/>Auth: oauth2-proxy
    IstioGW->>Proxy: Forward (mTLS)<br/>kubeflow-userid header
    Proxy->>DB: INSERT registered_model<br/>Auth: Username/Password
    DB-->>Proxy: Row created
    Proxy-->>IstioGW: 201 Created (JSON)
    IstioGW-->>Client: Response

    Note over Controller,DB: Flow 2: InferenceService Reconciliation

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch InferenceService CRDs<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: InferenceService event (CREATE/UPDATE)
    Controller->>Proxy: POST/PATCH /api/.../inference_services<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (mTLS)
    Proxy->>DB: Upsert inference service record
    DB-->>Proxy: Row upserted
    Proxy-->>Controller: 200 OK

    Note over CSI,S3: Flow 3: Model Download via CSI Storage Initializer

    KServePod->>CSI: Init container starts<br/>storageUri: model-registry://model/v1
    CSI->>Proxy: GET /api/.../model_artifacts/{id}<br/>Auth: None (same mesh)
    Proxy->>DB: SELECT artifact URI
    DB-->>Proxy: s3://bucket/model.tar.gz
    Proxy-->>CSI: Artifact metadata (storage URI)
    CSI->>S3: Download model artifacts<br/>Auth: Provider credentials (TLS 1.2+)
    S3-->>CSI: Model files
    CSI-->>KServePod: Model ready at /mnt/models

    Note over AsyncJob,Sigstore: Flow 4: Async Model Upload Job

    AsyncJob->>S3: Download model from source<br/>Auth: AWS IAM credentials
    S3-->>AsyncJob: Model artifacts
    AsyncJob->>OCI: Push model as OCI image (Skopeo)<br/>Auth: Docker config
    OCI-->>AsyncJob: Push complete
    AsyncJob->>Sigstore: Sign artifact (OIDC)<br/>Fulcio cert + Rekor log
    Sigstore-->>AsyncJob: Signature recorded
    AsyncJob->>Proxy: PATCH /api/.../model_artifacts/{id}<br/>Update URI + signature
    Proxy->>DB: UPDATE artifact record
    DB-->>Proxy: Updated
    Proxy-->>AsyncJob: 200 OK
